 * implement parser to parse http url, prefixed with http or https, ip address (ipv4 or ipv6) or hostname, optionally a colon and port, optionally a resource path, and optionally a path params list

 * implement stream to read/write websocket data -> you can test this with https://www.piesocket.com/websocket-tester client, after integration with Serc on serc-template-application
 * implement stream to read write server sent event data
